Market Capitalisation, end 1991:               Pounds 82.3bn
Inflation Rate, May 1992:                       5.6 per cent
Interest Rate (discount), June 1992:             12 per cent
Exchange Rate, Jun 15:                    Pounds 1 = L2207.8
