the Swiss Volks Bank (the bank) of Dollars 35.5m by dishonestly and falsely
representing to officers of the bank:
(i) That Robert Maxwell Group plc was the legal and beneficial owner of 2.4m
common shares in Berlitz International Incorporated (the shares).
(ii) That Robert Maxwell Group plc had the right to execute, deliver and to
