Mr Faisal Husseini, the leader of the Palestinian negotiating team, Mrs
Hanan Ashrawi, the spokeswoman, and Dr Haidar Abdel-Shafi, chief negotiator,
met and embraced Mr Arafat in front of the press.
Israeli jets raided alleged Hizbollah bases in south Lebanon yesterday, the
14th air raid in a month.
